+ What's This?

This is the Caretaker Theme by [[*user winkwonkboi]].

This theme is specially designed for articles pertaining to the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/anomalous-entity-engagement-division-hub Anomalous Entity Engagement Division (AEED),] a branch of the SCP Foundation.

+ How to Use

On any wiki, just apply the following code at the top of your page:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:caretaker-theme]]@@
[[/div]]

//Note: This is a Black Highlighter based theme, so be sure to include that theme too, as you can see right above me. To learn more, go [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:black-highlighter-theme here.]//

----

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/theme:caretaker-theme/feesh.png|caption=Wow, it's me!|width=300px]]

+ Examples

A horizontal rule can be created using five hyphens @@"-----"@@ and extends across the page if not placed inside, let's say, a blockquote. Lines separating sections of this page are horizontal rules.

[[collapsible show="+ Oh hey, a collapsible!" hide="- So this is what it looks like."]]
Titles can be created by putting between one and six pluses "+" at the beginning of the line.

+ First Title
++ Second Title
+++ Third Title
++++ Fourth Title
+++++ Fifth Title
++++++ And so on
[[/collapsible]]

